            <ul>
              <% @horoscopes.each do |horoscope| %>
              <li><%= link_to image_tag( "profile_square/#{horoscope.short_name}.png"), horoscope_path(horoscope) %></li>
              <% end %>
            </ul>
          </div>        
        </div>
      </div>  
      <div class="col">
        <div class="wrapper">
          <h3>Daily horoscope</h3>
          <p class="text-justify">
            A long long time ago in a galaxy far far away, a great group of warriors got together 
            to break down myths and bring to you the real facts about the zodiac. Although
            you may know them for other initiatives, even as enemies in occasions, let it be know that no one in 
            any galaxy knows the star's secrets better that them. Their union represent the ultimate
            alliance in astrology. <strong>Click on an image and see what the stars have to say.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
